{"tid":1044220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想回到過去","createTime":"2019-03-02T17:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T21:19:30.000Z","uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca57b4750a33b0e996847596b613e5a228af8db5","tid":1044220,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"過左8年幾，所有回憶都仲好似近日發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果可以時光倒流就好，就算係記憶重播都好，同佢一齊嘅日子係我人生唯一開心同最開心嘅時光，我根本接受唔到冇佢係我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《回到過去》<br />\n黑暗已在空中盤旋 該往哪我看不見<br />\n也許愛在夢的另一端 無法存活在真實的空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n...<br />\n想回到過去 試著讓故事繼續 至少不再讓妳離我而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9a994b14c68f70f33890a56f12462cd7a07afd","tid":1044220,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T21:19:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.com/albums/ah233/sorsawsor/47ce2da2_zps2uogydgn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1381.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F47ce2da2_zps2uogydgn.gif&h=e0908ef7&s={SIZE}\" /> 零回覆互助社溫馨回覆 <img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.com/albums/ah233/sorsawsor/47ce2da2_zps2uogydgn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1381.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F47ce2da2_zps2uogydgn.gif&h=e0908ef7&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}